name: Provence Cologne
description: In a tiny, collector's item bottle spills forth the luscious scent of Haute Provence in the height of summer. The sweet, herbaceous freshness of Lavender absolute intermingled with the finest French Lavender steam distilled oil will transport you to the purple azure grandeur of Provence. A hint of Sandalwood and Rose Damask rounds out this gorgeous , timeless fragrance.

name: Enchant Perfume
description: Long regarded as a scent of royalty, Neroli is truly a magical, hypnotic floral essence that characterizes this exquisite perfume. With hints of musk and rose, Enchant is a true gem. Available in limited edition 5ml bottle.

name: Cortona Cologne
description: Bursting forth with a symphony of Citrus reminiscent of a sun soaked summer's day in Tuscany, Cortona takes you there. A light, yet bold cologne infused with Lemon, Lime, Tuscan Orange and a hint of Sandalwood, Cortona is the scent of happiness. ( Note: All natural essential oils used in this gorgeous perfume can increase the effects of the sun on your skin so wear out of direct sunlight) 5ml Limited Edition Miniature Bottle.

name: Parfum de Morgaine
description: An intoxicating, sensual scent, Parfum de Morgaine will tantalize your senses with all natural notes of exotic Sandalwood, hint of Rose Damask, and Jasmine.  Like this perfume's namesake, Morgaine Le Fey, expect to feel magical and hypnotic! Perfect for layering or to wear alone for an intimate candlelight dinner. Available in the miniature collectible limited edition 5ml bottle.
